<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-162] migrate to junit</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-162</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;junit has a fork option which will allow our tests to be 100% independent of each other instead of sorta kinda independent.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12425156">CASSANDRA-162</key>
            <summary>migrate to junit</summary>
